This paper involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict personal attributes from text data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of word2vec, which is a popular technique in information retrieval and text mining, and thus, it could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Furthermore, the paper involves the analysis of large datasets, which could fall under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of personal attributes, which could also belong to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
